    <attracc>
      <attraccr>The expected accuracy of the measured variables is as follows: attitude within 0.05 degree, 3 centimeters nominal ranging accuracy, and vertical elevation accuracy of 15 centimeters RMSE for the submerged topographic surface. Quality checks are built into the data-processing software.</attraccr>
    </attracc>
