      <vertacc>
        <vertaccr>Typical vertical elevation accuracies for these data are consistent with the point elevation data; however, a ground-control survey is not conducted simultaneously with every lidar survey. Vertical accuracies may vary based on the type of terrain and the accuracy of the Geographical Positioning System (GPS) and aircraft-attitude measurements.</vertaccr>
      </vertacc>
